{"tid":1367724,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[遍地開花］一班年輕熱血老救 致香港人的公開信","createTime":"2019-07-26T10:39:02.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-27T06:48:41.000Z","uid":28248,"like":22,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"1ac0f95bc28caba8fbcf3bff6670e9db473f8c5f","tid":1367724,"uid":28248,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T10:39:02.000Z","msg":"致香港每一個市民<br />\n我地係一班熱血既年輕老救 <br />\n好想為個社會去出一分力 <br />\n雖然只係微不足道 冇消防救護咁偉大 <br />\n但我哋絕不好似警察不公執法 我哋一視同仁 <br />\n哪怕係唔同政見 當佢哋需要幫忙時絕對會伸出援手 唔會見死不救 絕對謹守崗位 盡忠職守<br />\n正所謂救人一命 勝造七級浮屠 <br />\n雖然我地唔係政府工種 <br />\n但絕不誣蔑其他紀律部隊嘅辛勞 <br />\n希望大家可以保持心態<br />\n不分化 不割席<br />\n<br />\n革命要成功 係需要一班志同道合既人一齊革命<br />\n<br />\n警署最愛落閘放狗<br />\n市民被毆絕不幫手<br />\n何妖吹雞周街劈友<br />\n差人見到掉頭就走<br />\n消防救護盡忠職守<br />\n制服小偷令佢敗走<br />\n我哋老救唔會係狗<br />\n九個字先嚟做小丑<br />\n需要幫手就即拯救！即拯救！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n屌你老母死黑警 pu你啊mo 你老母個羅<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/u3E3Piy.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fu3E3Piy.png&h=1fdf36fe&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8939ba510d654a4e203e2a998aabb702f6d8b117","tid":1367724,"uid":28248,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T10:42:29.000Z","msg":"請大家727出來"},{"pid":"cd5333084534d3ded4a2ec48ea77aba37481317f","tid":1367724,"uid":28248,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T10:42:40.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"219a1a68af9eb8c749cc1aa862a61edece32a84f","tid":1367724,"uid":48366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T10:51:18.000Z","msg":"多謝你"},{"pid":"8d910fbac124cd894303d775ac1c56803f403750","tid":1367724,"uid":278414,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T10:51:53.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"7cd6e13f8572d7db773b9d3973d214b347f5b4cc","tid":1367724,"uid":259675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T10:51:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dccfc6b78246fe1533d4035f48ec3489eb0d9c98","tid":1367724,"uid":261166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T10:53:38.000Z","msg":"同路人:<br />\n<br />\n花在盛放，請再開行業 TG group ，互通消息，<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">專業逆權，行內抗爭！<br />\n合縱連橫，團結抗爭！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n詳情：「遍地開花」合縱連橫，時機到了<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1363346\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1363346</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">統一戰線，五大訴求，不撤不退</span>"},{"pid":"83481287c26c1283cd62b98bfce1a78eaa239d56","tid":1367724,"uid":28432,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T10:56:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4e587d7ce9c0dbbf2bfd98c6a56efa3efaf58b2b","tid":1367724,"uid":28248,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T12:52:20.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"65750b451f0036294a6b591d947b252e5cdec356","tid":1367724,"uid":28248,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T16:28:09.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"8bcb0b9e1ccceb1731fea656801ea681b5df9df0","tid":1367724,"uid":28248,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T02:46:35.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"80789bbc995fb538eb923b6b8fdd28ebffd1f9e1","tid":1367724,"uid":164966,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T02:49:26.000Z","msg":"當緊更，陣間影相上嚟"},{"pid":"ab665b02f4549648608ff7707136671b8a888473","tid":1367724,"uid":28248,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"80789bbc995fb538eb923b6b8fdd28ebffd1f9e1","tid":1367724,"uid":164966,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T02:49:26.000Z","msg":"當緊更，陣間影相上嚟"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T03:08:56.000Z","msg":"